<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document Status Update</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #F39C12;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .status-info {
            background-color: #fff5e6;
            border: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .status {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #F39C12;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #F39C12;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Document Status Update</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{username}},</h2>
        <p>We're writing to inform you about an update to the status of your document in our verification system.</p>
        <div class="status-info">
            <h3>Document Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Document Title:</strong> {{documentTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>New Status:</strong> <span class="status">{{newStatus}}</span></p>
            <p><strong>Updated On:</strong> {{updateDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Updated By:</strong> {{updatedBy}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>{{statusMessage}}</p>
        <p>To view more details about your document and its verification status, please click the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{documentLink}}" class="button">View Document Details</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you're having trouble with the button above, you can also copy and paste the following link into your
            browser:</p>
        <p>{{documentLink}}</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this status update, please don't hesitate to contact our
            support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Document Verification System. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>